# uniCenta oPOS 4.2 â€“ Image Size Fix

**Bug**: editing a product repeatedly inflates the image BLOB size because
`Utilities.writeImage()` rewrites the buffer as PNG.

**Fix**: it now writes `"jpg"` instead of `"png"`.

## Downloads
See the assets of release **v4.2-imagefix**:
- Windows installer (.exe)
- Linux installer (.sh)
- Patched `unicentaopos4.2.jar`

## Source code
- Original uniCenta oPOS 4.2 source: https://sourceforge.net/projects/unicentaopos/
- This repository includes the modified source (if you chose Camino A) **or**
  a patch file (`imagefix.patch`) to apply over the original code (Camino B).

